{"tid":1661848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新戰線] 杯葛銀聯","createTime":"2019-10-18T11:14:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-19T04:08:44.000Z","uid":306193,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"aa715158a656c611f5546e917bb955fc263fb3b1","tid":1661848,"uid":306193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emFbjfG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemFbjfG.jpg&h=091d7536&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為左進一步阻止中国滲透，我地有必要係生活盡可能避免中国既野。而銀聯係中国既交易系統，類似VISA同MasterCard。<span style=\"color: red;\">而香港近年大部分既提款卡都係銀聯，甚至信用卡都銀聯。用信用卡比錢商戶要比錢就係人都知啦，咁既話錢又比銀聯。</span><br />\n<br />\n近年好多人去外國㩒錢，揸住張銀聯卡亞洲好多地方都可以㩒，但其實每次提款都會收你最少15蚊，而銀聯自己個兌換率係頗差架，換言之，每次㩒錢唱錢，銀聯袋唔少。<br />\n<br />\n所以，請大家唔好再用銀聯信用卡同提款卡。如果匯豐同渣打可以要求出張plus或者cirrus，又或者叫銀行放你個戶口落信用卡， 咁就唔使用銀聯啦。"},{"pid":"ae701991ccdaefb91a020742793524ba56a42eee","tid":1661848,"uid":233090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"路過一推"},{"pid":"654af7627bef434c5a0534bf85285080bdc6b681","tid":1661848,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:18:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e9215eefb5a65caf1fc778954c5581d8800c1308","tid":1661848,"uid":262379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:19:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f530dd642f42f2392f89f7ef6c119abcfb959a3","tid":1661848,"uid":233090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3b994058dbbd0bd02551ba2cd4d57834caadb226","tid":1661848,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"2f60c6be1a33fcec602e2da8d2cfed903d0b4d0d","tid":1661848,"uid":113929,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T11:31:35.000Z","msg":"銀聯真係垃圾， 去歐洲想揾部機都難"},{"pid":"3bf48f70682f425294c2daca138615a72f6f17fe","tid":1661848,"uid":233090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T03:59:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e877f2dc4aac594b7b0cec7502a01ec10948ed65","tid":1661848,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:02:46.000Z","msg":"有得轉既咩？<br />\n之前問極都無"},{"pid":"0b84b3b01b23ddf3842d1ad9cb169bba5f010158","tid":1661848,"uid":300915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:08:19.000Z","msg":"銀聯垃圾都爆，出左香港十部有九部提款機都用唔撚到。"},{"pid":"944cae866c8b0d12f64bbdd03681c4e04949701f","tid":1661848,"uid":278645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T04:08:44.000Z","msg":"巴打出篇文教唔用銀聯點樣可以喺外國ATM攞到錢, thx!"}]}